    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1938-01-15T08:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1938-01-15T08:00:00-05:00" n="851"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d851">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">833.5151/460: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Uruguay</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Reed</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Montevideo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-01-15T10:00:00-03:00"
                            >January 15, 1938—10 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received January 15—9:05 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>5. Unless otherwise instructed I shall defer compliance with Department’s
                    telegram No. 3, January 14, 4 p.m., until 19th in hope of action by Minister of
                    Finance.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Reed</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
